Walter Payton, John Stamos, Lynn Swann, Betty White, Hershel
Walker, Danny White, Mary Hart, Roger Miller, Chuck Woolery and
Oprah Winfrey.
   Sound like a lineup for a Bob Hope special?
   ``I wish,'' he said. ``Barbara can attract them, but she's an
attraction by herself.''
